SUMMARY:Board Game Night at Langers
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nCome play games and meet other local gamers at Langers Entertainment Center in Sherwood! Bring your own games or pick from a wide selection provided by the Museum of Gaming. Admission is free and family-friendly. Food can be purchased through Langers. Attendance averages 20 people.
