SUMMARY:Speed puzzle night
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nThink you’re the fastest puzzler in town? Join us for Speed Puzzling\, hosted by @portlandpuzzleco\, on Thursday\, Nov. 6th at 6:30 PM at Hillsboro Downtown Station! Complete a 500-piece puzzle as fast as possible (you keep the puzzle). $35 per team to play. 1st-place winner takes home $100!\nSIGN-UP ahead of time to secure your spot — walk-ins are welcome\, but extra puzzles are very limited. This competition is open to all ages. You can compete as a solo\, duo\, or team up! So bring your friends\, family\, your puzzle-loving crew\, or join a team and meet new friends.\nPre register at:\n[Speed Puzzling Hillsboro Downtown Station | Portland Puzzle Company](https://portlandpuzzle.com/speed-puzzling-hillsboro-downtown-station/)
