SUMMARY:Open Game Night
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nVisit Off the Charts Games\, a family run game store in Downtown Gresham\, every Friday for a night of board games and good company. Bring your favorite board game and some friends. No Sign up\, No cost\, Plenty of table space.
