SUMMARY:Super Mox Board Games
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nIf you have board games that you love to play -- please bring them.\nIf you are new to board games -- just bring your self\, and maybe a friend.\n\nDon't be shy\, just ask any table if they have room for another player.\nNote that sometimes other groups have meetups here too -- so ask for the "Super Board Game Meetup". \;)\n\nPlease be responsible and respectful in these interesting times\, we encourage all flavors of people to come by.\n\nIf you have any questions\, just ask for Joey at the Event or message me or the Organizers of this Group at any time.\n\nSee more events through the Calendar view = https://www.meetup.com/pdxgames/events/calendar/
